snippet.title: Encoded War - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2220070/Encoded_War/

Here is the 5-YEAR CONTRACT to get your son back. 
You must become the MORSE SENDER during World War II. 
Deliver our encoded messages and lead DEUTSCHLAND TO VICTORY!

TOP 50 overall of Ludum Dare 51
